HB 754 Original 2026 Regular Session Coates
Abstract: Create the Manchac Wildlife Management Area Sanctuary for marine life in
Lake Pontchartrain.
Present law creates sanctuary areas on Lake Pontchartrain and creates prohibitions for
catching certain fish and other marine life including prohibitions for certain equipment.
Proposed law retains provisions of present law and adds the Manchac Wildlife Management
Area Sanctuary.
(Amends R.S. 56:804(A)-(E))
